title: Looking for a duo to reach Gold

embed.description: Check your Summoner Stats/MMR, Live Spectate and using powerful global LoL Statistics!

body:
Hi all,

I am looking for a duo (or a team) to reach gold rank.
Someone who mains mid, adc or jungle is preferred.
I main top, rarely go mid.

Please let me know before adding me in game.

Thank you
